    "The prior width of station gain priors was similar to THEMIS in Sect. 5.1.4.",
    "A detailed description of the prior distributions is given in Appendix L.",
    "Finally, the un-normalized posterior was formed by taking a product of the prior and the likelihood distributions.",
    "To sample from the posterior, we used a two-stage strategy.",
    "First, to find a reasonable starting location, we adopted the L-BFGS optimizer (Liu & Nocedal 1989; Mogensen & Riseth 2018), running it 20 times, and initializing it from random draws from the prior."
